Class PacketData<T extends Packet>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ws2d.core.network.PacketData<T>
  • Type Parameters:

    public final class PacketData<T extends Packet>
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains metadata for a given packet type. This includes the class of the packet, the handler, and the packet ID.
